snippet.title: 狂ったリンボ／Loco Limbo
snippet.description: Loco Limbo is a fun indie game where you control a Character who can Detach and use their Limbs. Stuck on a weird island after military experiments, you solve puzzles and survive using your unique limb abilities. Can you make it off this crazy island in one piece?
